==English==

===Pronunciation===
*stā, /steɪ/, /<tt>steI</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-eɪ|Rhymes: -eɪ]]

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|stay||}}
# To [[remain]] in a particular place.  (''We stayed in Hawaii for a week.'')
# To [[continue]] to have a particular [[quality]].  (''Wear gloves so your hands stay warm.'')

